Norman: Blue Cod, huh? My pals used to see those so much more... Got poached to ablivion and now you barely see them. #portrait:norman
Sam: Really? What happened? #portrait:sam
Norman: Some businessman found out you could make jewelry with them, and everyone started netting them by the dozen at night. #portrait:norman
Norman: Totally destroyed the population... Now they're a pretty rare sight. #portrait:norman
Sam: Aww... what happened to the jeweler? #portrait:sam
Norman: Ran out of supply, so I guess he went and found something else to make his stones with. #portrait:norman
Sam: Huh... sounds like a bit of a strange guy... #portrait:sam

